Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:19.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《比利小子》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously on Billy the Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:22.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行走西部是件危险的事 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Travelin'west is a dangerous business, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:25.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,结局并不总是如我们所愿\N{\rYUANWEN}Things don't always end up the way we want'em to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}－ Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不是玩具\N{\rYUANWEN}This is not a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:33.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你不打算开枪 就别拿它指着人\N{\rYUANWEN}You never point that at a man unless you intend to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想做什么 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}What is it you want to be, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:43.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你已经是亡命之徒了 孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}You're an outlaw now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:45.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没什么选择了\N{\rYUANWEN}- You ain't got a lot of options. -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我还是想改邪归正 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}I still have a hankerin' to go straight, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这怎么可能呢 两个县都在通缉你\N{\rYUANWEN}How's that gonna happen? You're wanted in two counties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你已经出名了\N{\rYUANWEN}You're gettin' pretty famous now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:54.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的脸被贴的到处都是 你的事迹口口相传\N{\rYUANWEN}Your face is all over the place. People talk about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:55.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不在乎 我只知道\N{\rYUANWEN}That don't mean nothing to me. I sure as hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想因为杀人而出名\N{\rYUANWEN}don't wanna be famous for killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:02.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,托巴斯克小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Senorita Del Tobosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:04.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是想自我介绍一下\N{\rYUANWEN}I just wanted to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:08.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你以为我对这镇上的事一无所知吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you imagine I had no idea of what happens in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:13.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真为你汗颜\N{\rYUANWEN}Shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有个人墨菲 他在林肯开了家大商店\N{\rYUANWEN}This guy Murphy- - he owns a big store in Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们成立了一家名为浩世的公司\N{\rYUANWEN}They got a company called The House,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:20.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就通过墨菲的店经营\N{\rYUANWEN}and they run it outta Murphy's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 我很荣幸\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, Billy, I want to say it's a great honor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:24.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,终于见到你本人了 真是蓬荜生辉\N{\rYUANWEN}to finally meet you in the flesh. Great honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我的合伙人 约翰尼·莱利吉姆·多兰\N{\rYUANWEN}My partners here- Johnny Riley, Jim Dolan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我的王国 要真被英国混蛋夺走\N{\rYUANWEN}This is my kingdom. I'll be damned if I'm gonna let
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:31.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也就无颜活在世上了\N{\rYUANWEN}some prick Englishmen take it away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:33.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你也许见过街那头的那家新店\N{\rYUANWEN}You may have seen this new store down at the end of the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:35.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你到底在干什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What the hell are you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别跟我耍心眼儿 小子\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't get smart with me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 我们结束了\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey, we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有人可以先跟我断交 没有人\N{\rYUANWEN}No one...is gonna foreclose on us. No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:43.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你在威胁我们 你要是真想威胁的话\N{\rYUANWEN}You threathenin' us? Cause if you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也没人能打败我们\N{\rYUANWEN}And no one is gonna outgun us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:50.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我早劝你 别把粮食卖给汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}I told you not to sell grain to Tunstall, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你我有协议在先\N{\rYUANWEN}You have a contract with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:53.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是说 战争正在酝酿\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm talkin' about the war that's brewin',
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲和汤斯顿之间的战争\N{\rYUANWEN}the war between Murphy and Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲显然更有钱\N{\rYUANWEN}· Murphy's got the loudest pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 这些人 啥玩意儿也不是\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy, these people, they don't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:01.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我同意和汤斯顿见面\N{\rYUANWEN}I agree to meet with Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但必须秘密见面\N{\rYUANWEN}It has to be in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就是你等待一生的\N{\rYUANWEN}This is the time and place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:07.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个时刻 那个地点\N{\rYUANWEN}you have waited for all your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不再为墨菲少校干活了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm quittin'Major Murphy's payroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从英国人汤斯顿那里接了份工作\N{\rYUANWEN}I accepted a job with the Englishmen, Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:16.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你真以为我们会这么放了你\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you really think we're just gonna let you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让他走他吧 会有我们收拾他的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}Let him go his way. Our time will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是啊 会的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 我们走 快走\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay, let's go. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,晚上回来救你俩 好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You two, you're up next, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,翻过墙你就安全了 好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Over the wall and you're safe. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:42.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 我做不到\N{\rYUANWEN}－ Billy, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是唯一的出路 好吗查理 准备好了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}This is the only way, all right? Charlie. You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快走 快快快\N{\rYUANWEN}Go, go, go. Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:00.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rYUANWEN}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这帮混蛋\N{\rYUANWEN}You fuckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,强尼 桌子\N{\rYUANWEN}Johnny. Table!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,强尼 我们得走了 走吧 来\N{\rYUANWEN}Johnny, we gotta go! We gotta go. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:24.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗3 2 1\N{\rYUANWEN}You ready? 3...2...1.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们 我相信大家都知道我们来这儿的原因\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen, I believe we all know why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事实很明确 我们已经跟\N{\rYUANWEN}There is no hiding the fact that we are now effectively
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,与墨菲先生和浩世公司开战了\N{\rYUANWEN}at war with Mr. Murphy and the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我听说墨菲在扩充军队\N{\rYUANWEN}I hear Murphy's hiring more guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道 我也在招兵买马\N{\rYUANWEN}I know, but I've been recruiting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想你们已经认识\N{\rYUANWEN}I think you gentlemen have already made the acquaintance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弗雷德·怀特和约翰·米德尔顿了\N{\rYUANWEN}of Fred Waite and John Middleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对 我们基本上都认识\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah. We mostly all know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大多数人也知道胡安·佩特龙\N{\rYUANWEN}And most of you will also know Juan Patron,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是西裔社区的主要成员\N{\rYUANWEN}as a leading member of the Hispanic community.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是个重要成员 因为他能说服社区\N{\rYUANWEN}He's very important because he can persuade that community
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,信任并支持我们\N{\rYUANWEN}to trust and support us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我向各位保证\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, I promise you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:35.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我最不想看到枪火四起\N{\rYUANWEN}the last thing I want is a shooting match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但如果真到了那一天 我们必须做好准备\N{\rYUANWEN}But if it comes to it, we have to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,另外告诉大家 我要任命比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I want you all to know that I'm appointing Billy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为我的副手\N{\rYUANWEN}as my second- in- command.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不在时 大家听他的号令\N{\rYUANWEN}So, if I'm not around, you'll take your orders from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢您的好意 汤斯顿先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I thank you for your gesture, Mr. Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我认为这个职位应该交给迪克·布鲁尔\N{\rYUANWEN}But I think you should give the job to Dick Brewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:03.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 既然你真这么想我就同意了\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course. If that is your wish, Billy, I concur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:07.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 大家明确一下前进的方向\N{\rYUANWEN}So, let's be clear about the way forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:11.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会被墨菲和他的爪牙吓到\N{\rYUANWEN}I will not be intimidated by Murphy and his crooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:17.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恰恰相反 这让我进一步放手发展事业\N{\rYUANWEN}On the contrary, I intend to pursue my business freely- -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会扩大商店\N{\rYUANWEN}expanding my store,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:22.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,增加牲畜 甚至开一家新银行\N{\rYUANWEN}my cattle stock, and even opening a new bank- -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为林肯人民提供更便捷的贷款\N{\rYUANWEN}a bank that will offer the people of Lincoln
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,逃离浩世公司\N{\rYUANWEN}easy credit and a way of escaping
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,腐败的商业剥削\N{\rYUANWEN}- the House's corrupt business practices. -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是我扫大家的兴 汤斯顿先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want to be the fly in the ointment, Mr. Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我得提醒一下 墨菲家族颇有些有权有势的朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}But I must remind the meeting that Murphy still has powerful friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们不仅是在挑战浩世公司\N{\rYUANWEN}We're not just taking on the House here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也是在挑战圣达菲圈\N{\rYUANWEN}We're also taking on the Santa Fe Ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这下性质就完全不一样了\N{\rYUANWEN}and that is a different proposition altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真的很感激您的提议 汤斯顿先生\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, I really did appreciate the offer, Mr. Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但布鲁尔比我来的时间更长\N{\rYUANWEN}But Brewer's been here longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他了解您的运营方式 手下也信任他\N{\rYUANWEN}He knows your operation, and the men trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你支持他 我自然也会支持他\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, if he has your support, he'll certainly have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,知道吗 小子们\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西·埃文斯屠杀那家农户\N{\rYUANWEN}… maybe Jesse Evans went too far,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:34.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,连孩子都不放过 可能有点太过分了\N{\rYUANWEN}killing those farmers, even their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把我的名声和生意拖下了水 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Dragging my name and my business through the mud, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿是想从内部分裂我们\N{\rYUANWEN}Tunstall is trying to break us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rYUANWEN}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\rYUANWEN}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我打个响指就能毁掉汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}I can ruin Tunstall just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所有想破坏我生意的人 都是一样下场\N{\rYUANWEN}Same way I ruined anybody else who tried to muscle in on my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不光是你的生意了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's no longer your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:58.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们买了你的股份记得吗现在是我们的生意\N{\rYUANWEN}We bought you out, remember? And right now, our business
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,濒临破产\N{\rYUANWEN}is staring bankruptcy right in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:04.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要对付的不只是汤斯顿和几个当地农户\N{\rYUANWEN}We're not just dealing with Tunstall and a few local farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他已把比利小子招致麾下\N{\rYUANWEN}He has Billy the Kid working for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:11.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那又怎样 你不们明白 我又不想打仗\N{\rYUANWEN}So? You don't get it. I don't want a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没有选择 我们得到消息\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't have a choice. We have information that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿想在本地开银行\N{\rYUANWEN}Tunstall wants to open up a bank here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:19.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们最大的债主 托马斯·卡特伦\N{\rYUANWEN}Our biggest lender, Thomas Catron, who just happens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也就是卡特伦银行和信托的总裁\N{\rYUANWEN}to be the President of Catron Bank and Trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,绝对不希望看到这一幕\N{\rYUANWEN}isn't exactly gonna like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道卡特伦是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}I know who Catron is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得提醒你 我和卡特伦先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Need I remind ya's that Mr. Catron and I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是老朋友了 我们仍然一起做生意\N{\rYUANWEN}are old friends and that we still do business together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦会对付那个银行的\N{\rYUANWEN}Catron will deal with the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-即便如此  -天\N{\rYUANWEN}Even so- - - Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们真是俩开心果啊\N{\rYUANWEN}So, the two of you make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真他妈让我发笑\N{\rYUANWEN}You make me fuckin' laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:47.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们开玩笑呢吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you kiddin'me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你真的认为他们会在林肯\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you really think that they're going to open up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:53.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,开银行吗 真的吗 为谁而开\N{\rYUANWEN}a bank here in Lincoln? Really? Who for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这里大多数人是墨西哥 而且穷得要命\N{\rYUANWEN}Most of them are Mexicans and piss poor, for Christ's sakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我倒要问问 他们要银行干什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What in the name of God do they need a bank for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能告诉我吗 嗯\N{\rYUANWEN}Will you tell me that, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,管好那个杰西·埃文斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Keep Jesse Evans on a leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都下去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}We're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你愿意和我一起出来 我很开心\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm glad you wanted to ride out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你为啥觉得我不会 就因为你是逃犯\N{\rYUANWEN}Why did you think I wouldn't? Because you're an outlaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,虽然我已经不是了\N{\rYUANWEN}Although I'm not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿先生帮我处理好了\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Tunstall saw to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是好事啊 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm so happy to hear that, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你父母呢 他们也会觉得是好事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What about your parents? Will they be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们家族依然深受西班牙裔影响\N{\rYUANWEN}My family still has a strong Spanish heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们的观念更传统一点\N{\rYUANWEN}They are tied to the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:50.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你自己呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为还是应该是适应新生活方式\N{\rYUANWEN}I think it's better to adapt to this new way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们也改变不了 但他们不同意\N{\rYUANWEN}We can't change it, but they don't agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过去对他们来说太重要\N{\rYUANWEN}The past is so important to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我听到了些传闻\N{\rYUANWEN}I hear things,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我担心 如果谣言属实\N{\rYUANWEN}and I'm scared that if the rumors are true,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:15.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可能被卷入这两大商行的斗争\N{\rYUANWEN}we may all be dragged into war between these two shopkeepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不会有事的\N{\rYUANWEN}Nothing will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\rYUANWEN}Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:25.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不如你我回马厩看看\N{\rYUANWEN}Why don't you come back and see the stables with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你父母呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What about your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:27.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们不在家\N{\rYUANWEN}They're not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:49.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-谢谢   -谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}- Gracias. - Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说的是西班牙语\N{\rYUANWEN}- It's Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,安达卢西亚马\N{\rYUANWEN}An Andalusian horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我亲自训练的他\N{\rYUANWEN}I broke and trained him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:19.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\rYUANWEN}Ven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\rYUANWEN}Ven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真棒\N{\rYUANWEN}Bonita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过来 来\N{\rYUANWEN}Ven. Vamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rYUANWEN}Muy bien.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对了\N{\rYUANWEN}Eso.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好神奇\N{\rYUANWEN}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you. -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\N{\rYUANWEN}Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们还没互相认识过\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't think we've, uh, been introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这位是巴克赛特·罗伯茨\N{\rYUANWEN}This here is Buckshot Roberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:51.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是我们的人了 一个神枪手\N{\rYUANWEN}He's joined us. He's an amazing sharpshooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 罗伯茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, it's a pleasure to meet you, Mr. Roberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有什么要告诉我们的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You have something to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们跟墨菲先生聊过了\N{\rYUANWEN}We met with Mr. Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他觉得自己做得过分了\N{\rYUANWEN}He thinks he might have gone a little bit far,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不想和汤斯顿开战\N{\rYUANWEN}and he doesn't want to wage a war with Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这老醉鬼真他妈宅心仁厚啊 上帝保佑\N{\rYUANWEN}Seems the old drunk's got a tender conscience, God help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托 明眼人都知道我们已经开战了\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on, we all know that we're already at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我调查汤斯顿的生意好久了\N{\rYUANWEN}I've been checking out Tunstall's operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道他把牛马养在什么地方\N{\rYUANWEN}and I know where he keeps most of his cattle and his horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:23.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要是我们开战 搞个突然袭击如何\N{\rYUANWEN}If we're going to war, what say we raid'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,突袭\N{\rYUANWEN}Raid'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那么好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们同意\N{\rYUANWEN}We're agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但要先等等\N{\rYUANWEN}But hang fire for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别给汤斯顿留下诉诸法律的机会\N{\rYUANWEN}We don't want to give Tunstall any excuses to go to the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我们在这里干嘛\N{\rYUANWEN}Then what the fuck are we doin'here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,埃文斯先生 你们在这里\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, what you're doing here, Mr. Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要盯着你朋友比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}...is you're gonna keep an eye on your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为他是我们所有人的威胁\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy the Boy, cause he's a danger to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别担心 埃文斯先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't you worry, Mr. Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有你过瘾的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}You'll get your excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,查理 你知道跟浩世公司的生意\N{\rYUANWEN}Charlie, you know this business with the House
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最后会很难收场 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}might get messy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你老婆刚怀了第一个孩子 你输不起的\N{\rYUANWEN}With your wife carryin' your first child and all, you got a lot to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不能一走了之\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不能在这个时候\N{\rYUANWEN}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来吧 好姑娘\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on, girl. Attagirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过来 女孩 来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Here, girl. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你死了\N{\rYUANWEN}If you get killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我该对这个遗腹子说些什么\N{\rYUANWEN}… what do I tell the child who will never meet their father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你终于像个战士了 查理\N{\rYUANWEN}You look like a soldier now, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:28.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这很奇怪 比利 但我觉得我早就认识你了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's...it's strange, Billy, but I...I feel like I know you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 我知道这不可能\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course, I don't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-说说你自己吧  -你想听什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell me something about yourself. - What is there to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟我说说你的家庭吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, tell me about your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:47.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我家里有母亲 父亲 我哥哥乔\N{\rYUANWEN}I had a mother, a father, little brother Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们都死了\N{\rYUANWEN}They all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在英国有三个姐妹\N{\rYUANWEN}I have three sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她们对我来说\N{\rYUANWEN}back home in England, and.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是整个世界\N{\rYUANWEN}they all mean the world to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我妈妈这个人很特别\N{\rYUANWEN}My mom was a very special person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她眼中的世界与大多数人不同\N{\rYUANWEN}Saw the world different to most.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只是没能活下去\N{\rYUANWEN}Just didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没必要抱歉\N{\rYUANWEN}No need to be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你给了我机会 让我过上了已经不再奢望的生活\N{\rYUANWEN}You've given me a chance at a life I'd almost stopped believing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你必须相信 比利 你必须保持信念\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, you must believe in it, Billy, you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,每个人都值得第二次机会\N{\rYUANWEN}Everyone deserves a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:43.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我知道你为了投奔我 放弃了很多\N{\rYUANWEN}But I- - I know you gave up a lot to join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的那些朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}You had friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西 当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟他交情很深\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse and I go a long way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他总喜欢游走在法律之外\N{\rYUANWEN}He always liked living outside the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我才来投奔你的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\rYUANWEN}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请允许我自我介绍下\N{\rYUANWEN}Allow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我叫埃德加·华尔兹\N{\rYUANWEN}My name is Edgar Walz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是托马斯·卡特伦先生的女婿\N{\rYUANWEN}I am the son- in- law of Mr. Thomas Catron,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也是他的经纪人\N{\rYUANWEN}as well as his agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:21.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那么 我想你们应该就是\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, I presume you are.
