Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.71,0:27:36.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,针对粮食和牲畜的极低定价\N{\rYUANWEN}The fixing of low prices for grain and cattle
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.21,0:27:38.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,使许多农民陷入贫困\N{\rYUANWEN}has reduced many of the farmers to penury.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.42,0:27:42.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们代表这些农户 正在发起一场\N{\rYUANWEN}On behalf of those farmers, we are instigating
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.97,0:27:45.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对浩世的法律诉讼\N{\rYUANWEN}legal proceedings against the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.51,0:27:47.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,多亏了老威尔逊法官\N{\rYUANWEN}And thanks to old Judge Wilson,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.72,0:27:49.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我被任命为副警长\N{\rYUANWEN}I've been appointed Deputy Sheriff,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.73,0:27:51.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,尽管布雷迪警长表示反对\N{\rYUANWEN}despite the objections of Sheriff Brady.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.86,0:27:59.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我越来越相信\N{\rYUANWEN}You know what? I'm really startin' to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.32,0:28:00.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿可以赢了\N{\rYUANWEN}that Tunstall can win this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.90,0:28:02.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rYUANWEN}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.16,0:28:03.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说呢 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}What say you, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.62,0:28:06.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,讲真吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.37,0:28:10.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果真要发生枪战\N{\rYUANWEN}If it comes to a shooting war,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.66,0:28:12.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,优势在另一方\N{\rYUANWEN}the other side has the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.08,0:28:14.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们只是农民\N{\rYUANWEN}You're farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.92,0:28:17.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西·埃文斯和他的部下都是职业杀手\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse Evans and his gang are all practiced killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.92,0:28:19.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们不会把我们放在眼里的\N{\rYUANWEN}They got to be thinking we're easy meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.30,0:28:23.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没想到你会说这种丧气话\N{\rYUANWEN}That's not exactly what I wanted to hear comin'from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.93,0:28:27.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托 乔治 你不能逃避事实\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on, George, you can't hide from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.35,0:28:29.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但还有另一个事实\N{\rYUANWEN}But there's another truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.60,0:28:33.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,普通人也能做出不平凡的事\N{\rYUANWEN}Ordinary folk can perform extraordinary deeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.90,0:28:35.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,尤其在有信仰加持时\N{\rYUANWEN}especially if they believe in something,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.90,0:28:37.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我相信汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}and I believe in Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.69,0:28:39.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我相信他跟墨菲和达菲圈开战\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe he's doing the right thing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.32,0:28:40.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是在行正义之事\N{\rYUANWEN}fighting Murphy and the Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.49,0:28:42.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会为他的事业而战\N{\rYUANWEN}And I will fight for his cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.66,0:28:47.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 能私下聊聊吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, Billy, can I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.08,0:28:54.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想跟你说件事\N{\rYUANWEN}There was just, uh, one other thing I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.46,0:28:59.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西·埃文斯对我们威胁极大\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse Evans is a real danger to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.34,0:29:02.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有没有可能说服他\N{\rYUANWEN}Is there any way, perhaps, that you can persuade him
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.30,0:29:03.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别为墨菲做事了\N{\rYUANWEN}not to work for Murphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.39,0:29:08.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,考虑一下吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Just...think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.35,0:29:12.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.68,0:29:53.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,查理\N{\rYUANWEN}Whoa, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.27,0:29:56.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rYUANWEN}I think it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.82,0:30:07.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小朋友 过来\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey, kid, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.87,0:30:16.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你叫什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.00,0:30:20.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗨 我叫汤姆·奥福利亚德\N{\rYUANWEN}Hi. My name's, uh, Tom O'Folliard.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.55,0:30:27.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是比利小子 对吗\N{\rYUANWEN}And, uh, you're Billy the Kid, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.05,0:30:30.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.18,0:30:35.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道你是 我看过你的画像\N{\rYUANWEN}I know you are. I've seen your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.64,0:30:37.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和你一模一样\N{\rYUANWEN}Looks just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.77,0:30:40.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你从哪来\N{\rYUANWEN}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.98,0:30:43.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,德克萨斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.07,0:30:46.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利是我的英雄\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy's my hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.86,0:30:51.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我走了好远 来加入他的帮派\N{\rYUANWEN}I come a long way to join his gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.28,0:30:53.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我这一辈子的梦想\N{\rYUANWEN}It's all I want in my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.66,0:30:57.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我发誓 我不会麻烦你的 让我做什么都行\N{\rYUANWEN}I won't be no trouble, I swear. I'll do anything you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.58,0:30:59.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恐怕你白跑这么远了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm afraid you've made a long journey for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.58,0:31:01.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已经没有帮派了\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't have a gang anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.71,0:31:05.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且你来的也不是时候\N{\rYUANWEN}And you came here at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.63,0:31:08.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯县现在很危险\N{\rYUANWEN}It's gettin' real dangerous here in Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.88,0:31:10.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不在乎真的\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't mind, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.18,0:31:12.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我只想跟着你干  -我在乎\N{\rYUANWEN}- I just want to be with you. - I mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.64,0:31:16.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还小 还是个孩子 我不想看你受伤\N{\rYUANWEN}You're young. Just a kid. I don't want to see you gettin'hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.89,0:31:20.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或者死掉 回家吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Or killed. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.69,0:31:23.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你父母肯定担心坏了\N{\rYUANWEN}Your parents must be worried sick about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.32,0:31:27.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走吧 回去\N{\rYUANWEN}Go on. Get!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.62,0:31:39.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.92,0:31:44.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上一次好好吃饭是什么时候\N{\rYUANWEN}When's the last time you ate properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.42,0:31:50.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行吧 跟我们来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right. Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.30,0:31:52.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,吃饱了再上路\N{\rYUANWEN}We'll get you fed, then you're on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.10,0:31:58.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你到底为什么离开家\N{\rYUANWEN}Why'd you really leave home?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.02,0:32:02.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和我说说你家人\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell me about your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.40,0:32:05.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rYUANWEN}I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.11,0:32:09.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道我爸是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know who my father was.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.15,0:32:12.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我妈再婚了\N{\rYUANWEN}My mother married again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.24,0:32:16.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,继父是个酒鬼\N{\rYUANWEN}My stepfather, he was a...he was a drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.41,0:32:18.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很暴力\N{\rYUANWEN}A real violent man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.45,0:32:20.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打我妈\N{\rYUANWEN}Attacked my ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.41,0:32:24.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,酒后暴打\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, in a drunken rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.55,0:32:30.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把她脑子都打出来了\N{\rYUANWEN}Beat her brains out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.30,0:32:34.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打得她奄奄一息\N{\rYUANWEN}Left her dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.35,0:32:38.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 我没有\N{\rYUANWEN}You see I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.27,0:32:42.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没有家\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't have a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.98,0:32:45.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没有亲人\N{\rYUANWEN}You know I don't have anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.20,0:32:54.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们不收留我 我只会死在山沟里\N{\rYUANWEN}You send me away, I'll just die in a ditch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.45,0:32:56.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.25,0:33:01.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,其实\N{\rYUANWEN}You know I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.87,0:33:05.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,见到你我很开心\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm so happy I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.71,0:33:08.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.63,0:33:10.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我该走了 我不想\N{\rYUANWEN}Now I should go. I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.71,0:33:12.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再浪费你们时间\N{\rYUANWEN}waste any more of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.09,0:33:14.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢招待\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.05,0:33:18.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别走了 汤姆\N{\rYUANWEN}You're not going anywhere, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.73,0:33:26.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,留在这里吧\N{\rYUANWEN}We can put you up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.19,0:33:29.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我教你经营农场 怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}I'|I teach you ranching. How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.20,0:33:35.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.03,0:33:37.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.22,0:33:57.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.01,0:34:01.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他说墨西哥人会用\N{\rYUANWEN}He said the Mexicans would use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.73,0:34:14.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是达尔西妮亚 她旁边的是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}That's Dulcinea. Who's that with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.62,0:34:19.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,查理\N{\rYUANWEN}Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.20,0:34:23.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听说她订婚了\N{\rYUANWEN}I heard she's engaged to be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.04,0:35:06.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威尔逊法官\N{\rYUANWEN}Judge Wilson?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.80,0:35:20.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威尔逊法官\N{\rYUANWEN}Judge Wilson...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.18,0:35:22.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我 我是亚历山大·麦克斯文\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm...I'm Alexander McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.18,0:35:24.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,约翰·汤斯顿的律师\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm the lawyer working for John Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.81,0:35:32.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我记得你以前是给墨菲少校干活儿的\N{\rYUANWEN}I remember you used to work for Major Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.90,0:35:35.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那时我还不知道他集团的真面目\N{\rYUANWEN}That's before I knew the truth about his organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.65,0:35:39.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或许你应该观察得再仔细一点\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, maybe you should have looked more closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.99,0:35:43.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道你很了解\N{\rYUANWEN}I know you're familiar with what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.53,0:35:45.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿先生和墨菲浩世公司之间的恩怨\N{\rYUANWEN}between Mr. Tunstall and Murphy's House.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.87,0:35:48.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事实是 我必须在法庭上\N{\rYUANWEN}Fact is, I'm going to have to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.83,0:35:51.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,与墨菲之家作斗争\N{\rYUANWEN}House's corrupt practices through the courts
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.17,0:35:53.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,揭露他们的腐败行径 终结这一切\N{\rYUANWEN}in order to expose and end them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.17,0:35:54.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或许你也清楚\N{\rYUANWEN}But as you are probably also aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.71,0:35:59.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯县的大部分法院和法官都已被腐蚀\N{\rYUANWEN}most of the courts and judges in Lincoln are themselves corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.77,0:36:18.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对付墨菲很危险 但我必须这么做\N{\rYUANWEN}Taking on Murphy was dangerous, but I was compelled to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.95,0:36:24.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也正因如此 我的儿子在某个周日晚上\N{\rYUANWEN}And as a consequence, my son was cut down
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.91,0:36:27.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,倒在了一场枪战中\N{\rYUANWEN}in a hail of bullets one Sunday evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.87,0:36:32.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很遗憾\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.84,0:36:39.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想 你是希望我帮你\N{\rYUANWEN}But I guess you want me to help you file charges
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.63,0:36:41.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在法庭上向尚存正义的法官\N{\rYUANWEN}against the House in courts
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.59,0:36:44.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,起诉浩世\N{\rYUANWEN}and in front of judges that just might still be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.26,0:36:46.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.72,0:36:49.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的先生 这正是我的想法\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir. That- - that would be my hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.35,0:36:53.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我只能告诉你 麦克斯文先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, all I can tell you, Mr. McSween,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.35,0:36:57.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我对圣塔菲圈子恨入骨髓\N{\rYUANWEN}is that I hate the Rings with every fiber of my being.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.94,0:37:03.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在我看来 圣塔菲圈子污染了美国生活的方方面面\N{\rYUANWEN}It's my belief that the Rings have polluted every aspect of American life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.20,0:37:04.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为什么一群有钱人\N{\rYUANWEN}How come groups of rich men
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.86,0:37:07.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能决定对和错\N{\rYUANWEN}get to decide what's right and what's wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.74,0:37:09.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,决定谁生谁死\N{\rYUANWEN}who lives and who dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.33,0:37:12.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是对美国的背叛\N{\rYUANWEN}That's a betrayal of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.46,0:37:16.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要还有一口气 我就会抗争到底\N{\rYUANWEN}And as long as I have breath in my body, I will resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.63,0:37:22.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我回答了你的问题了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Have I answered your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.97,0:37:25.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.68,0:37:30.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,驾 驾\N{\rYUANWEN}Hyah! Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.74,0:37:53.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你来这里干什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What the fuck are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.37,0:37:56.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想让你不要再为墨菲做事了\N{\rYUANWEN}I came to ask you if you'd stop working for Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.54,0:37:59.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在就抽身吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Just walk away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.67,0:38:02.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他和魔鬼一样狡猾 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}He is as crooked as the devil, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.01,0:38:04.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你又是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, and who are you? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.31,0:38:14.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大天使加百列吗 呵\N{\rYUANWEN}The fucking archangel Gabriel? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.27,0:38:19.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是关心你 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Look, I- - I care about you, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.69,0:38:24.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-是吗    -真的\N{\rYUANWEN}- Is that right? - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.15,0:38:28.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,经历了这些 你可能觉得我不在乎你了 但不是这样的\N{\rYUANWEN}It may not seem that way after everything we've been through, but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.54,0:38:37.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谁让你来的 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Who told you to come here, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.42,0:38:39.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的新朋友汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}Your new friend Tunstall?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.84,0:38:47.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你练得怎么样了\N{\rYUANWEN}How's your practicing coming on?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.76,0:38:50.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还记得我们以前比过一次吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You remember we did this once before?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.68,0:38:54.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-杰西  -是\N{\rYUANWEN}- Jesse- - Um, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.56,0:38:57.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是为了某个女孩\N{\rYUANWEN}It was about some girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.65,0:39:00.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,记得吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.65,0:39:02.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我记得\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:06.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道你记得\N{\rYUANWEN}I know you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.88,0:39:25.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你要开枪打我吗 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}You gonna shoot me, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.34,0:39:28.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Go on. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.39,0:39:36.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来啊 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.78,0:39:48.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你会开枪吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Would you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.82,0:39:53.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想我们永远不会知道答案\N{\rYUANWEN}I guess we'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.20,0:39:58.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已经有答案了\N{\rYUANWEN}I got my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.93,0:40:13.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,回见 小子\N{\rYUANWEN}See you later, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.01,0:40:53.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,埃德加·华尔兹先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Edgar Walz, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.84,0:40:55.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.64,0:40:59.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说说吧 林肯县之行如何\N{\rYUANWEN}So tell me, how was your visit to Lincoln?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.23,0:41:02.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,非常顺利 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}It went very well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.56,0:41:07.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我见了浩世的老板 多兰和莱利\N{\rYUANWEN}I met with the owners of the House, Dolan and Riley
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.94,0:41:10.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我和他们说了 你对目前\N{\rYUANWEN}and, um, told them how unhappy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.82,0:41:12.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,的情况很不满意\N{\rYUANWEN}you are with the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.61,0:41:13.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,银行的事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}With the bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.36,0:41:17.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的先生 尤其对银行不满 尤其是银行\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir, especially with the bank. Especially with the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.16,0:41:21.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们保证 银行马上就会关门\N{\rYUANWEN}But they assured me that it will soon be shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.87,0:41:23.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-所以  -很好\N{\rYUANWEN}So...- Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.67,0:41:28.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好 肯定不止这些吧\N{\rYUANWEN}That's good. There must be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.46,0:41:31.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的先生 当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir. Of course. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.67,0:41:35.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我去了没多久\N{\rYUANWEN}So shortly after my visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.97,0:41:39.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,多兰就被浩世除掉了\N{\rYUANWEN}Dolan was removed from the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.47,0:41:41.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从现在开始 我们只要应付莱利就好\N{\rYUANWEN}From now on, we only have to deal with Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.72,0:41:43.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好 没关系 他就是个打掩护的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, that's fine. He's just a straw man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.40,0:41:49.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可爱的女儿怎么样了\N{\rYUANWEN}How's my lovely daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.36,0:41:53.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么我好久都见不到她一次\N{\rYUANWEN}How come I never get to see her? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.57,0:41:57.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道的 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}You know what it's like, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.24,0:42:00.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她 她是个老师\N{\rYUANWEN}She's a...teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.12,0:42:05.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她当然也希望能经常见你\N{\rYUANWEN}But, um, of course she would like to see more of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.46,0:42:06.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但抽不出时间\N{\rYUANWEN}It takes up her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.29,0:42:11.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对 她压根儿不在意 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Right. She could give a fuck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.50,0:42:13.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是的 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}No, no, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.30,0:42:18.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是的 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}"No, sir. "
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.01,0:42:22.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是的 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}"No, sir. "
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.31,0:42:31.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,埃德加 我了解你们所有人\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, Edgar, I can understand all you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.15,0:42:35.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道莱利和多兰是不择手段的人\N{\rYUANWEN}I knew that Riley and Dolan were chancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.32,0:42:37.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道墨菲成天喝酒成性\N{\rYUANWEN}I know that Murphy's fucking sick with drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.61,0:42:39.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我才好心\N{\rYUANWEN}which is why I choose to keep him in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.91,0:42:41.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没动他\N{\rYUANWEN}for sentimental reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.83,0:42:45.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但有个人我不理解\N{\rYUANWEN}There's someone I don't understand- -
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.46,0:42:47.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个人让我很感兴趣\N{\rYUANWEN}someone who really interests me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.54,0:42:51.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我老听人提起他 但我不知道他是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}I hear his name everywhere, but I have no idea who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.42,0:42:54.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也不知道他想要什么\N{\rYUANWEN}or what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.43,0:43:01.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这人叫 比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm talking about the man they call... Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.43,0:43:06.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,著名的法外之徒\N{\rYUANWEN}The famous outlaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.44,0:43:11.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我对他一无所知 但他却扰得我不得安宁\N{\rYUANWEN}I know jack shit about him, and already he haunts my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.74,0:43:22.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这人突然出现 似乎要改变一切\N{\rYUANWEN}Suddenly, someone walks in who seems to change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.37,0:43:26.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我满脑子想的都是 他真的是我的敌人吗\N{\rYUANWEN}And all I'm thinking, is he my real enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.04,0:43:29.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要对付他吗 你懂吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do I have to deal with him? You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.59,0:43:35.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-是的先生  -去搞清楚\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir. - Find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.47,0:43:40.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要知道 这比利小子到底是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Find out 'cause I need to know who the hell is Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.01,0:43:46.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我怎样才能接近他\N{\rYUANWEN}How can I get to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.74,0:44:02.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.04,0:44:11.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过来 让我看看你\N{\rYUANWEN}Come closer. Let me see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.59,0:44:16.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果不打算开枪\N{\rYUANWEN}You never point a gun at anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.38,0:44:18.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就别拔出来指着别人\N{\rYUANWEN}unless you mean to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.01,0:44:20.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,老莫斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Old Moss?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.60,0:44:30.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你怎么在这里  -我路过\N{\rYUANWEN}- What are you doin' here? - I just come by to see how
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.52,0:44:32.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来看看你 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}you were gettin'on, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.65,0:44:37.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我一直没有忘记你\N{\rYUANWEN}Ain't never forgotten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.69,0:44:41.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们走在山间小道上 仿佛就是昨天\N{\rYUANWEN}Seems like yesterday, we was on the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.11,0:44:44.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你那时还是个孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}You, just a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.87,0:44:50.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我也没有忘记你  -轻一点\N{\rYUANWEN}- I ain't never forgotten you either. - Gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.21,0:44:52.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我欠你一条命\N{\rYUANWEN}I owe you my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.46,0:44:57.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你过得怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}How are you gettin'by?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.67,0:45:00.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就那样吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, oh, middling. You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.09,0:45:05.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我一直在报纸上关注你的消息\N{\rYUANWEN}But I've been, uh, followin your fortune in the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.14,0:45:11.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你似乎终于找了一份体面的工作\N{\rYUANWEN}Seems you got yourself a good and decent job at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.85,0:45:15.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 我要\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, I'm tryin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.19,0:45:17.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要让我妈为我骄傲\N{\rYUANWEN}I tryin' to make my ma proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.07,0:45:22.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是能闯出天地的人 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}You're a survivor, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.20,0:45:30.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我见到你的那一刻 我就知道了\N{\rYUANWEN}I knew that the moment I saw ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.54,0:45:34.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,记住\N{\rYUANWEN}Just remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.71,0:45:41.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事情不会总如你所愿\N{\rYUANWEN}things don't always turn out the way you want'em to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.97,0:45:51.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等 莫斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Wait, Moss.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.10,0:45:53.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让我进入你的灵魂\N{\rYUANWEN}Let me in your soul.
